title: FURINNO Simplistic Study Table, Light Blue
description: Time to get to work! Whether you are starting out on your latest DIY masterpiece or just having a seat while penning an important to-do list, this desk is always a delightful spot to do it. The Furinno Study table is a budget-friendly and unfussy addition to your space, while its clean-lined silhouette makes it easy to blend into any aesthetic. The study table is made of CARB-grade composite wood tested for durability and sturdiness. A simple attitude toward lifestyle is reflected directly in the design of Furinno Furniture, creating a trend of simple nature. Assembly is easy with provided step-by-step instructions. Care instructions: wipe clean with a clean damped cloth. Avoid using harsh chemicals. Pictures are for illustration purposes. All décor items are not included in this offer. The product is entitled to a 1-year warranty against manufacturer defects.
